  "Was identical to the EU ETS": "",
  "Legally mandated emission reduction targets with five-year carbon budgets": "",
  "Only addressed transportation emissions": "",
  "The UK Climate Change Act was groundbreaking as the first national legislation to set legally binding long-term emission reduction targets, originally 80% by 2050 and later amended to net-zero, with five-year carbon budgets providing clear milestones.": "",
